Queenite
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:(? journalists' name for) a North Island Maori loyal to the Queen (Victoria)
Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: a =FRIENDLY (cp KINGITE, from which it was probably formed)
